The daily opening times of American Museum of Natural History in New York

The following overview lists the visiting hours for American Museum of Natural History in New York. The hours of the current day (today) are highlighted. Please note that opening hours on special days or holidays may differ from what is displayed here. We therefore recommend you to always check the opening hours with American Museum of Natural History before your visit and see if it might be needed to reserve a time slot.
